//                      (Diakrisis 108.T premise).
//   Definition 10.2 вҖ” class `\cS_S^\cE` of S-definable enactments.
//   Lemma 10.3      вҖ” enactment syntaxвҖ“semantics: formal-S-definable
//                      enactment вҹ№ in `\cS_S^\cE^{global}` (post-audit
//                      C-7 explicit construction of (О№, r) via Kan
//                      extension + AdГЎmekвҖ“RosickГҪ adjoint-functor
//                      existence).
//   Theorem 10.4    вҖ” **AC/OC Morita Duality**: `рқ”җ вүғ_{(вҲһ,вҲһ)} рқ”җ_\cE`
//                      via Оө вҠЈ Оұ biadjunction. Centrepiece, parallels
//                      Theorem 5.1 / 6.1 / 9.3 on dual side.
//   Corollary 10.5  вҖ” `Con(\cF вҲӘ \cE) = Con(\cF) = Con(\ZFC + 2-inacc)`.
